OL,3,CWoman who took own life told friend of
OL,4,Chusband's alleged abuse, jury told
OL,6,FA woman who took her own life told a
OL,7,Ffriend she had suffered abuse at the
OL,8,Fhands of her husband, who is now on
OL,9,Ftrial for manslaughter, a court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FChristopher Trybus, of Swindon,
OL,13,FWiltshire, is accused over the death
OL,14,Fof Tarryn Baird, who died in November
OL,15,F2017 at the age of 34.
OL,17,FTrybus, 43, also faces charges at
OL,18,FWinchester Crown Court of controlling
OL,19,Fand coercive behaviour and two charges
OL,20,Fof rape, alleged to have happened in
OL,21,FOctober and November 2016.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
