OL,3,CWoman who took own life told friend of
OL,4,Chusband's alleged abuse, jury told
OL,6,FMrs Clarke described how they had
OL,7,Fbonded over their husbands both being
OL,8,F"workaholics" and maintained their
OL,9,Ffriendship when Ms Baird left the
OL,10,Fcompany.
OL,12,FText messages between the women were
OL,13,Fread by Tom Little KC, prosecuting,
OL,14,Fwith Ms Baird first alleging abuse by
OL,15,Fher husband in January 2017.
OL,17,FIn one exchange, Ms Baird described
OL,18,Fhow Trybus had "snapped" and showed a
OL,19,F"different side" of himself to her.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@MO]zD@POUzD@XO]{D@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
