OL,3,CWoman who took own life told friend of
OL,4,Chusband's alleged abuse, jury told
OL,6,FOn April 3, Ms Baird wrote to her
OL,7,Ffriend: "Hey Libby, I hope you guys
OL,8,Fare having a good day. Please could
OL,9,Fyou do me a favour. If it ever comes
OL,10,Fup, please say I was with you today.
OL,11,FIt will probably never come up but
OL,12,Fjust in case, I just want to cover
OL,13,Fmyself. Thanks."
OL,15,FWhen asked what had happened, Ms Baird
OL,16,Freplied: "Chris tracked me at the
OL,17,Fhospital so need cover. Just a bit
OL,18,Fbruised and sore but I will heal, I
OL,19,Falways do."
OL,26,@oD@IOUuD@PO]xD@JOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
