OL,3,CWoman who took own life told friend of
OL,4,Chusband's alleged abuse, jury told
OL,6,FGiving evidence, Mrs Clarke confirmed
OL,7,Fshe had met Ms Baird every "couple of
OL,8,Fweeks" in 2017 and they were more in
OL,9,Ftouch that year "because she was going
OL,10,Fthrough so much".
OL,12,FMr Little asked about Ms Baird's
OL,13,Fdrinking and whether it had been
OL,14,Fdiscussed.Mrs Clarke replied: "Yes, I
OL,15,Fknow there was a conversation that
OL,16,Ftook place. It would have been after
OL,17,Fshe disclosed it to me because she
OL,18,Fgave me a reason for why she was
OL,19,Fdrinking. She said that when
OL,20,FChristopher hurt her, it numbed the
OL,21,Fpain."
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@FO]qD@QOUrD@PO]vD@_OU}D@FO]
