OL,3,CWoman who took own life told friend of
OL,4,Chusband's alleged abuse, jury told
OL,6,FWhen asked what she meant, Mrs Clarke
OL,7,Freplied: "Being beaten."
OL,9,FRepresenting Trybus, Katy Thorne KC,
OL,10,Fasked Mrs Clarke to confirm that
OL,11,FTrybus and his wife lived in a big
OL,12,Fhouse, drove Porsche vehicles and had
OL,13,F"fancy holidays". Mrs Clarke said this
OL,14,Fwas the case, and also confirmed she
OL,15,Fbelieved Ms Baird was "rattling around
OL,16,Fin a big house on her own".
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@XO]uD@AOUuD@PO]wD@WOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
