OL,3,CWoman who took own life told friend of
OL,4,Chusband's alleged abuse, jury told
OL,6,FShe added that Ms Baird's alcohol
OL,7,Fconsumption was "like a housewife
OL,8,Fhaving a drink" and not noticeable to
OL,9,Fthe point she would have picked up on
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,FEarlier in the trial, Mr Little
OL,13,Falleged that Trybus carried out
OL,14,F"extensive and escalating controlling,
OL,15,Fcoercive and manipulative behaviour
OL,16,Fincluding sexual violence".
OL,26,@oD@QOUpD@OO]vD@AOUxD@ZO]
