OL,3,CWoman who took own life told friend of
OL,4,Chusband's alleged abuse, jury told
OL,6,FHe said the prosecution's case is that
OL,7,FTrybus, who travelled abroad regularly
OL,8,Ffor his work as a software consultant
OL,9,Fand developer, is "legally
OL,10,Fresponsible" for Ms Baird's death.
OL,12,FTrybus and Ms Baird, both from South
OL,13,FAfrica, moved to the UK in 2007 and
OL,14,Fmarried in 2009.
OL,16,FHe denies the charges and the trial
OL,17,Fcontinues.
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@LO]
